<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-82-0696 </DOCNO><TEXT>Energy Options was designed as an opportunity for Canadians to engagein an examination of energy issues. This report reflects the views expressedby Canadians in the conferences, seminars and papers that made up theEnergy Options dialogue. The following topics are covered: a statementon energy and Canadians; energy and development; energy security; energyand the environment; energy and markets; energy and the fiscal system;energy efficiency; energy and technology.</TEXT></DOC>